name: Moving in Depths
description:
Creator: Oslo Grace

This photograph represents the freedom, fluidity, and energetic weight held in both my chest and larger transition as a trans person. Having access to this piece will be maintaining a bookmark in this snapshot of time, one where I am at the crux of young adulthood, rising out of a childhood where things were much more painful. My chest represents the commitment to my own heart I had to make to arrive where I am at—autonomous, understanding, happy, and grateful within my identity.
